description: The newest rival to Jughead’s eating contest crown, Toni Topaz is a tough girl who sports pink hair with her purple jumpsuit. She finally met her competition at a cupcake-eating contest, where Jughead was surprised to discover that his sister Jelly Bean had run off. Toni offered her assistance along with her sarcastic BFFs Snarky and Hammer. Jug forfeited the challenge after finding Jelly Bean, and Toni still hopes to defeat him one day.
